      "message": "[Critical] Line 1748: This gate uses Manager::autoLoad, but the conversation module\u0027s normal startup loading is controlled by autoLoadConversations_. If autoLoadConversations_ is false, doRegister() can still synchronously load conversations for a deferred disabled account, violating lazy-loading mode and the comment above. Use the same flag as convModule() so disabled accounts preserve the client\u0027s explicit no-autoload behavior.\n```suggestion\n    if (autoLoadConversations_ \u0026\u0026 isUsable())\n        if (auto* cm \u003d convModule())\n            cm-\u003eloadConversationsIfNeeded();\n```",
